<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>English Town - 영어가 쉬워지는 곳</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700;800&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            primary: '#2563eb',
            accent: '#fbbf24',
            sky: '#0ea5e9',
          },
          fontFamily: {
            display: ['Poppins', 'sans-serif'],
            sans: ['Noto Sans KR', 'sans-serif'],
          }
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body class="bg-white font-sans">

  <!-- Nav -->
  <nav class="bg-white shadow-sm sticky top-0 z-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <div class="text-3xl">🌎</div>
        <span class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-primary">English<span class="text-sky">Town</span></span>
      </div>
      <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600">
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-primary transition">프로그램</a>
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-primary transition">레벨테스트</a>
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-primary transition">수강후기</a>
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-primary transition">학원소개</a>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <a href="tel:02-1234-5678" class="hidden sm:flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
          <span>📞</span> 02-1234-5678
        </a>
        <button onclick="showModal()" class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-accent text-gray-900 font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-yellow-400 transition shadow-lg shadow-accent/25">
          무료 상담
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary via-sky to-blue-400"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\"><circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"40\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"0.5\" opacity=\"0.1\"/></svg>'); background-size: 100px;"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="text-white">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur rounded-full text-sm mb-6">
            ⭐ 수강생 만족도 98.7%
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-display font-extrabold mb-6 leading-tight">
            Speak English<br>
            <span class="text-accent">With Confidence!</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            20년 전통의 검증된 커리큘럼으로<br>
            3개월 안에 영어 자신감을 키워드립니다.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <button onclick="showModal()" class="px-8 py-4 bg-accent text-gray-900 font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-yellow-400 transition shadow-xl flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
              <span>무료 레벨테스트</span>
              <span>→</span>
            </button>
            <button class="px-8 py-4 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-white/30 transition">
              프로그램 보기
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl p-6 transform rotate-3 hover:rotate-0 transition duration-500">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522202176988-66273c2fd55f?q=80&w=600" class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-2xl mb-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="flex -space-x-2">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 rounded-full border-2 border-white"></div>
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-500 rounded-full border-2 border-white"></div>
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-500 rounded-full border-2 border-white"></div>
              </div>
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">12,000+ 수강생이 선택했습니다</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Floating Elements -->
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-4 animate-bounce">
            <div class="text-2xl">🎯</div>
            <div class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-800">목표 달성률</div>
            <div class="text-lg font-bold text-primary">94%</div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 bg-accent rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-4">
            <div class="text-2xl">🏆</div>
            <div class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-800">BEST 학원</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-bold">5년 연속</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Programs -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">맞춤형 영어 프로그램</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">나에게 딱 맞는 과정을 선택하세요</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition cursor-pointer group" onclick="showModal()">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition">
            💼
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">비즈니스 영어</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">회의, 프레젠테이션, 이메일 작성 등 비즈니스 현장에서 바로 활용 가능한 영어</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>✓ 1:1 맞춤 수업</li>
            <li>✓ 실무 시뮬레이션</li>
            <li>✓ 원어민 피드백</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary">3개월</span>
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary/10 text-primary font-semibold rounded-full text-sm">월 39만원</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-sky rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl text-white transform md:scale-105 cursor-pointer" onclick="showModal()">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 px-3 py-1 bg-accent text-gray-900 font-bold rounded-full text-xs">BEST</div>
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6">
            🎓
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">토익/토플 집중반</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-100 mb-4">목표 점수 달성을 위한 체계적인 커리큘럼과 실전 모의고사</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-blue-100 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>✓ 점수 보장제</li>
            <li>✓ 매주 모의고사</li>
            <li>✓ 1:1 약점 분석</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold">2개월</span>
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-white/20 font-semibold rounded-full text-sm">월 49만원</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition cursor-pointer group" onclick="showModal()">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition">
            ✈️
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">여행 영어</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">해외여행에서 자신있게 소통할 수 있는 실용 영어 회화</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>✓ 상황별 회화</li>
            <li>✓ 롤플레이 수업</li>
            <li>✓ 소규모 그룹</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-600">1개월</span>
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-green-100 text-green-700 font-semibold rounded-full text-sm">월 29만원</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Modal -->
  <div id="modal" class="fixed inset-0 bg-black/50 z-50 hidden flex items-center justify-center p-4">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 max-w-md w-full shadow-2xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-6">
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4">📝</div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">무료 레벨테스트 신청</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">10분 테스트로 나의 영어 실력을 확인하세요!</p>
      </div>
      <form onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('신청 완료! 곧 연락드리겠습니다 📞'); hideModal();">
        <input type="text" placeholder="이름" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl mb-3 focus:outline-none focus:border-primary">
        <input type="tel" placeholder="연락처" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl mb-3 focus:outline-none focus:border-primary">
        <select class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl mb-4 focus:outline-none focus:border-primary text-gray-600">
          <option>관심 프로그램 선택</option>
          <option>비즈니스 영어</option>
          <option>토익/토플 집중반</option>
          <option>여행 영어</option>
        </select>
        <button class="w-full py-4 bg-primary text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-700 transition">
          무료 신청하기
        </button>
      </form>
      <button onclick="hideModal()" class="w-full mt-4 text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700 transition text-sm">닫기</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    function showModal() {
      document.getElementById('modal').classList.remove('hidden');
    }
    function hideModal() {
      document.getElementById('modal').classList.add('hidden');
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
